1974 BMW E3 30s Manual:

Exquisitely Refurbished BMW 3.0L E3 Manual

Behold a classic masterpiece, meticulously reengineered with it's vintage charm. This BMW 3.0L E3, now Stroked to 3500 cc capacity, a seamless conversion from automatic to manual transmission, offering an unparalleled driving experience. 

The car has undergone an extensive overhaul, with a new clutch, gearbox, and differential—all fine-tuned to a shorter final drive ratio for improved response and agility. The prop shaft has been refurbished with new center bearings, and it rides on new shocks and rear wheel bearings. 

The suspension system has been enhanced with new control arm bushes, tie rod ends, and center drag link. New drive shafts ensure smooth power delivery, while the stainless steel exhaust and new brakes with flexible hoses promise a symphony of performance. 

Braking is more responsive with new front discs, and the vehicle sits proudly on 7x14” copy Alpina wheels, enveloped in premium Michelin tires. The full tool kit is intact, and the exterior is complemented by an optional passenger door mirror, adding a touch of symmetry and style.

Underneath, the drive shafts and fuel tank have been overhauled, with the alternator and power steering pump meticulously refurbished.

This BMW is more than a car; it's a statement. Don't miss the chance to own a piece of automotive history.

Please feel free to contact any of our sales people for further Information.

The Bentayga S takes the power and capability of the Bentayga and adds edgier, sportier performance and styling. With large 22” wheels and black styling details to add definition, powered by a twin-turbocharged 4.0 litre V8 engine with a sports exhaust and Bentley’s enhanced Sport Mode. The addition of all-wheel steering enables you to manoeuvre with greater ease, while also benefiting from more stability. Packed with cutting-edge digital technology, It includes Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, both wired or wireless, so you can integrate your phone easily.
